png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"177eb3a2c5993cb57cd9f01e7514b9c9dc4283d2","tid":1540964,"uid":110867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:07:18.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"84397396ef129aa2acc4b689ab10fafc2556772f","tid":1540964,"uid":110867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"49bf3ab1d5cfa4a8b6a454d1fedd9f017db009c9","tid":1540964,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>缺一不可</strong></span></span><br />\n咪撚改口號<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">送中仲未正式撤回 依家只係動議</span></span><br />\n<blockquote>林鄭又想過鳩我地一棟啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539720</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母仲要等復會 再提出撤回議案<br />\n而立法會復會係10月9或10月16日<br />\n重點就係呢到：10月1國慶<br />\n今日無啦啦出黎廢up<br />\n擺明就係想側側搏 係10月1日前盡快平息件事<br />\n等佢可以平平安安渡過鄰國國慶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求下你地睇埋呢篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家點睇脫共？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536794</a>"},{"pid":"f1671102db87eb64375a0b523947a561ec9073f0","tid":1540964,"uid":110867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"a4076a90f3f7fd3becd92e00c916d648670f0d1b","tid":1540964,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:08:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66d295b2b953ae7e83386c0ed8cb2ba8421d0b9f","tid":1540964,"uid":35696,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:08:36.000Z","msg":"我認為和理非回合先<br />\n表示民意冇逆轉過，爭取勇武本錢"},{"pid":"7d3058d56e0744390a8dd7d0ec80fab31e02fd